                      <p>I am currently doing research with Professor <a href="http://www.cs.rochester.edu/~kautz/">Henry Kautz</a>, where we <a href="http://www.cs.rochester.edu/~kautz/socialhealth/index.html">mine Twitter data to track the spread of diseases</a>. I am also a TA and Workshop Leader for two undergraduate Computer Science courses, and am the <a href="http://csug.rochester.edu/ugc/tutoring">Tutoring Chair</a> for the University's <a href="http://csug.rochester.edu/ugc">Computer Science Undergraduate Council</a>.</p>
